TITLE: Oathkeeper Access Rule Example with Header Mutator (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: A JSON representation of an Oathkeeper access rule employing the header mutator. It adds X-User and X-Some-Arbitrary-Data headers to the outgoing request, using Go text/template to extract values from session data. Required dependency: Oathkeeper running with proper access rule support. Inputs: matching HTTP requests; outputs: transformed requests with additional headers.
