SOURCE: https://github.com/ory/docs/blob/master/docs/kratos/self-hosted/15_mfa.mdx#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
# ...
selfservice:
  flows:
    settings:
      required_aal: highest_available
# ...
session:
  whoami:
    required_aal: aal1
# ...
```

