DESCRIPTION: This shell command utilizes the Ory CLI's `patch` command to modify the OAuth2 configuration of a project. It specifically targets the `/urls/self/issuer` path to replace its value with the new desired URL, typically the primary custom domain.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ory/docs/blob/master/docs/oauth2-oidc/issuer-url.mdx#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: shell
CODE:
```
