SOURCE: https://github.com/ory/docs/blob/master/docs/hydra/guides/cookies.mdx#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: YAML
CODE:
```
# SameSite=none requires HTTPS, so we need to disable dev mode:
dev: false

serve:
  cookies:
    same_site_mode: None
    same_site_legacy_workaround: true

```

