TITLE: Mixing Username and Email Identifiers in Ory Kratos Identity Schema (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This schema demonstrates using both 'email' and 'username' as alternative login identifiers in Ory Kratos. Each property supports password, webauthn, totp, code (for email), and passkey, along with email-based recovery and verification for the email field. Input must provide both 'email' (string, validated as email) and 'username' under 'traits'. Ory Kratos and JSON Schema draft-07 are required.
