TITLE: Ory CLI - Create Salesforce Connected App and Configure OAuth Callback
DESCRIPTION: Procedures for setting up Salesforce OAuth via CLI, including creating a connected app, setting the callback URL, and integrating claim mappings. The snippet provides a Jsonnet code for claims transformation, which must be encoded and included in configuration.
