DESCRIPTION: Uses the PATCH method with a JSON PATCH payload to add a new SSO OIDC connection to an Ory project configuration. Requires PROJECT_ID, WORKSPACE_API_KEY, the JSON payload conforming to the Ory API structure, and the Content-Type header. The payload includes parameters like client_id, client_secret, organization_id, and provider, among others. The jq utility is used to filter the resulting JSON output to relevant data.
