TITLE: Adding Cookie Mutator to a Per-Rule Access Rule (YAML)
DESCRIPTION: This YAML access-rule example includes a per-rule cookie mutator definition, showing how to add dynamically-populated cookies to requests for specific access rules by using Go template expressions. Dependencies: Oathkeeper, session-based templating. Inputs: session; outputs: transformed requests with cookies.
