TITLE: Advanced Ory Kratos Identity Schema with Multiple Traits (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This extended JSON Schema defines an advanced Ory Kratos identity with various traits including email (with multifactor support), nested name structure (first, last, nickname), age, newsletter subscription, and enterprise customer flags. It demonstrates comprehensive credential strategies and enforces 'email' as a required field while disallowing additional arbitrary properties under 'traits'. Requires Ory Kratos and JSON Schema with support for property nesting, booleans, and integers.
