TITLE: Handling Native App Callback with Expo WebBrowser in TypeScript (TSX)
DESCRIPTION: This React Native component (TSX) handles the deep link (`return_to` URL) received after successful social authentication. It uses Expo's `WebBrowser.maybeCompleteAuthSession` to potentially close the browser tab and signal completion of the flow initiated by `openAuthSessionAsync`. It's responsible for extracting the second part of the exchange code from the URL.
