TITLE: Configuring Hardware Security Module Environment Variables for Ory Hydra in Shell
DESCRIPTION: This shell snippet provides environment variable configuration to enable HSM support in Ory Hydra. It sets the HSM enablement flag, specifies the vendor PKCS#11 library path, token label or slot number, user PIN, and key set label prefix for multi-instance environments. These variables direct Ory Hydra to connect and operate with a specific HSM token for cryptographic key storage and operations.
