TITLE: Displaying GDPR Compliance Tabs - Dealing with Citizens
DESCRIPTION: MDX code block that creates a tabbed interface showing GDPR regulations related to dealing with citizens, Ory's supporting role, and customer responsibilities. The tabs display tables with compliance requirements and support levels.
