--keypairgen --key-type rsa:4096 --usage-sign \
--label hydra.openid.id-token --id 746573742d6b65792d6964

Key pair generated:
Private Key Object; RSA
  label:      hydra.openid.id-token
  ID:         746573742d6b65792d6964
  Usage:      sign
