TITLE: JSON Schema for Identity Traits with MFA Identifier Traits
DESCRIPTION: Defines the identity schema with email and phone traits, marking the email as the primary identifier for email MFA via 'code' method and phone via 'sms'. These properties are validated with formats and constraints, ensuring correct identification traits for MFA workflows.
