TITLE: Configuring OAuth2 Introspection Authenticator in an Access Rule
DESCRIPTION: This YAML snippet shows how to configure the `oauth2_introspection` authenticator specifically within an Oathkeeper Access Rule (`access-rule-1.yaml`). It includes rule-specific settings like required scope, target audience, trusted issuers, pre-authorization, and how to extract the token, potentially overriding global configurations.
