TITLE: Generating System Secret via urandom (Bash)
DESCRIPTION: Generates a random 32-character alphanumeric string using /dev/urandom and exports it as the SECRETS_SYSTEM environment variable. This variable is essential for Ory Hydra to encrypt data stored in the database and must be set to the same value every time the Hydra server restarts.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ory/docs/blob/master/docs/hydra/self-hosted/configure-deploy.mdx#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
