TITLE: Creating Relationships via CLI - Bash
DESCRIPTION: This Bash snippet demonstrates the usage of the Ory Keto CLI to create relationship tuples.  It parses policies files (alice_policies or bob_policies) from JSON format to create relation tuples using the `keto relation-tuple create` command.  Error handling is included using `>/dev/null` to suppress output and `&&` and `||` to display a success or failure message.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ory/docs/blob/master/docs/keto/guides/migrating-legacy-policies.mdx#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
