TITLE: Native App Authentication Flow Diagram
DESCRIPTION: A Mermaid sequence diagram illustrating the step-by-step interaction between the user, native app, browser, Ory Network, and the Identity Provider during the native app social sign-in process.
SOURCE: https://github.com/ory/docs/blob/master/docs/kratos/social-signin/96_native-apps.mdx#_snippet_1

