TITLE: Extended Backus-Naur Form (EBNF) Notation
DESCRIPTION: Defines the notation used throughout the specification to describe the language syntax using Extended Backus-Naur Form (EBNF).
SOURCE: https://github.com/ory/docs/blob/master/docs/keto/reference/ory-permission-language.mdx#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: ebnf
CODE:
```
Production  = production_name "=" [ Expression ] "." .
Expression  = Alternative { "|" Alternative } .
Alternative = Term { Term } .
Term        = production_name | token [ "…" token ] | Group | Option | Repetition .
Group       = "(" Expression ")" .
Option      = "[" Expression "]" .
Repetition  = "{" Expression "}" .
```

LANGUAGE: ebnf
CODE:
```
|   alternation
()  grouping
[]  option (0 or 1 times)
{}  repetition (0 to n times)
```

