SOURCE: https://github.com/ory/docs/blob/master/docs/kratos/reference/configuration.mdx#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: Markdown
CODE:
```
<ConfigMarkdown src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ory/kratos/master/.schemastore/config.schema.json" binary="kratos" />
```

